      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"BakeryCompositing-Compositing\">Compositing</h3><p>Once the AOVs have been Denoised, I use the Light Groups to rebuild the beauty pass in Nuke. This allows me to make modifications directly to the lights, be it exposure, tint, or contrast.</p><p>For further stylization,  the shadows have been tinted blue and the highlights have a slight orange and violet tint, which help accentuate the sensation of warmth. Before merging the layers, I use the Cryptomattes on certain glass objects whose brightness overpowers the image. To accomplish this, all I have to do is lower their reflection in the Light Groups and their specularity in the LPEs. Once the depth of field has been set using the Z pass in the utilities, it's time to merge the layers!</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"french-bakery-raw-render.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621053/french-bakery-raw-render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657621053/french-bakery-raw-render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621063\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"french-bakery-raw-render.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657621053\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1f89508b-a6a4-4bb1-a8bd-e35c4e54fdb2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621053/french-bakery-raw-render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621053/french-bakery-raw-render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p /><p>The next step is to accentuate the viewing direction by using a Grade node where we can lower the gamma. The resulting contrast focuses attention on areas of light.</p><p>The Glow and eFibonacciGlow nodes enable me to intensify sunlight by giving it a glow and simulating a lens smear, which gives the scene a dreamy look. To prevent the light from diffusing into shadows areas, it's important to isolate these highlights in a mask with the Keyer node.</p><p>Finally, we recreate the chromatic aberrations of a camera, apply lens vignetting, and a touch of grain to the image. Enjoy playing with the project!</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"french-bakery-comp.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621053/french-bakery-comp.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657621053/french-bakery-comp.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"french-bakery-comp.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657621053\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"15ae9956-2591-41fc-bd00-11853315d1af\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621053/french-bakery-comp.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621053/french-bakery-comp.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589647394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p /><hr/>"
